# 🧠 Project 7: Customer Segmentation & Retention Analysis

## 📊 Project Overview
This final capstone project analyzes customer behavior for a food delivery service, focusing on identifying high-value segments based on age, region, and repeat order frequency. The objective was to uncover trends in customer loyalty, retention gaps, and potential marketing opportunities using Power BI.

<p align="center">
  <img src="./7_1.PNG" alt="Customer Segment Dashboard" width="600">
</p>

---

## 📁 Data Sources
The dataset (`delivery_customers.xlsx`) includes:
- `customers`: Age, gender, region, signup date
- `orders`: Purchase date, order frequency, total spent
- `regions`: Urban/rural classification and population metadata

---

## ❓ Business Questions Answered
- Which age group generates the most revenue?
- Which regions have the highest repeat order rates?
- Do specific days or categories influence higher engagement?

---

## 🛠 Key Tasks and Methodology
### 📌 Retention Analysis
- Created calculated columns to identify repeat purchasers
- Built a matrix to calculate retention by cohort month
- Grouped customers by acquisition month to evaluate loyalty trends

### 🗺 Regional Revenue Insights
- Analyzed total revenue and monthly trends by region
- Used Power BI maps and filters to uncover geographic patterns

### 👥 Age Group Purchase Trends
- Compared average and total revenue by age segment
- Evaluated repeat purchase likelihood across customer demographics

<p align="center">
  <img src="./7_2.PNG" alt="Age Group Revenue Chart" width="600">
</p>

---

## 💡 Key Insights
- Customers aged 25–34 generated the highest total revenue and had strong repeat order activity
- Urban regions demonstrated higher overall order volume, but rural regions showed stronger loyalty among returning users
- Certain customer cohorts, particularly those acquired in Q2, showed significantly better retention metrics

---

## 🧰 Tools Used
- Power BI (DAX, Visualization, Cohort Analysis)
- Excel (Data prep & validation)

---

## 📦 Deliverables
- 🎯 Customer Segment Dashboard
- 📈 Age Group and Region Insights
- 🔁 Retention Cohort Matrix
- 📝 Executive Summary with KPIs and business recommendations
